nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Traitor (Talking Book Publishers Inc. audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Traitor is the unabridged audiobook version of the Star Wars Legends novel of the same name, by author Matthew Stover. The audiobook was performed by David Hartley-Margolin and released by Talking Book Publishers Inc. in 2005.
